              	<div class="block-item odd">
                  <h2>Art in the Allison Library</h2>
                  
                  
                       
                       <p>The Allison Library exhibits work from a different artist several times a year. Watch this space for information on our upcoming exhibitions.</p>
                  
                  <p>We also have a collection of permanent art in the library, featuring works by David Robinson, Tim Botts, and Freidrich Peter.</p>
                       
                  <div class="clearfix"></div>
                </div>
