                 <div class="five columns right-sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-content hours">
              <h3>Library Hours</h3>
              		<p>The circulation desk closes 10 minutes before the library closes. Please check out all materials prior to this time. The circulation desk is closed for chapel on Tuesdays from 11am to noon during the regular term.</p>
              		<h4>Regular term hours</h4>
              		<table height="98" width="206"><tbody><tr><td>Monday-Thursday
      </td>
      <td>
        8am - 10pm
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        Friday
      </td>
      <td>
        8am - 5pm
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        Saturday
      </td>
      <td>
        9am - 5pm
      </td>
    </tr>
